  <name>gnollama</name>
  <shortdesc xml:lang="en">gnollama, a Gnome based Ollama UI</shortdesc>
  <description xml:lang="en">
A GNOME based user interface to Ollama. Supports connecting to models from any host. Both Ollama "generate response" and "chat" APIs.
Supports choosing multiple images to send in the prompt.
Supports rendering Markdown and code highlighting in responses.
Saves chat history and allows management of saved chats.
Supports all settings in the Ollama API including images, system prompt, Thinking mode, Log probabilities, Temperature, etc..
  </description>

